title: Google searches on refugees and niqab trend during election campaign
text: As election day nears, Google searches on the refugee crisis and the niqab are on the rise, while those on the environment are dropping. With less than a week to go in the campaign, Google Canada has released data on the top trending and declining issues of the election. ...
